STATE of North Carolina
v.
Brian Joshua BAKER. No. 254P06. Supreme Court of North Carolina. June 29, 2006. Brian Joshua Baker, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, R., Stuart Albright, District Attorney, for State of NC.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Defendant on the 9th day of May 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Guilford County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 29th day of June 2006."
